                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 839.00/812.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">American Chargé d’Affaires</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-03-24">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 24, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The revenue cutter <hi rend="italic">Algonquin</hi> will proceed at once to
                    Dominican waters to establish radio communication with the <hi rend="italic"
                        >Wheeling</hi>.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Adee</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
